{"tid":1375052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撚狗魔法書] 呼籲大家download狗例魔法書傍身","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:21:42.000Z","uid":278201,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bfebda5c93603eaa2fac6a911085159ba1700c1d","tid":1375052,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知狗例列明曬狗圈限制就唔洗多講<br />\n但係實際上嘅條文 我相信唔係每個人都背到曬出嚟<br />\n依家同我download曬下面嘅警例佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Fpgo.html&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=4441066d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/pgo.html</a><br />\n特別係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第20章</span></strong></span><br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拒絕出示委任證或者表明身份</span>嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">同我無限loop依句：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根據警察通例第x章第x條，(成句條文) </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">第20章第3條：要求警犬披露身份</span></span><br />\n在不損害行動效率的情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\">人員於行使其法定權力時</span>，在市民要求下應披<br />\n露足以辨別其身分的個人資料。人員按要求表明身分後，應最低限度透露以下資料:<br />\n警員、警長、交通督導員及 高級交通督導員： <span style=\"color: red;\">職級及警務處職員編號</span><br />\n警署警長 及以上職級 :<span style=\"color: red;\">職級及姓氏 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azqKNbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazqKNbV.jpg&h=efeef765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第20章14條：要求出示委任證</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">第2項：便衣狗/無證狗</span><br />\n只要擬進行的工作不妨礙人員妥為保管委任證，<span style=\"color: red;\">警務人員在任何時候均須隨<br />\n身攜帶委任證</span>。<span style=\"color: red;\">便衣人員</span>不論是否當值，在<span style=\"color: red;\">與巿民接觸</span>和<span style=\"color: red;\">行使警察權力</span>時，<span style=\"color: red;\">必須表明身<br />\n分及出示委任證</span>。在<span style=\"color: red;\">案發現場的便衣人員</span>，須<span style=\"color: red;\">將委任證掛在顯眼的地方</span>，讓人易於辨認其身分。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">第4項：軍裝狗</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員應出示委任證</span>，除非： <br />\n(a) 情況不容許；或 <br />\n(b) 出示委任證會影響警隊行動及／或危及有關人員的安全；或 <br />\n(c) 要求不合理。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">第5項</span>：如軍裝警務人員在上文第4(a)及(b)段的情況下未能按要求出示委任證，<span style=\"color: red;\">其後<br />\n待情況許可便應即時出示委任證</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過要注意軍裝狗有特例</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">第5項</span>: 如一隊軍裝警務人員執行任務，例如在查核牌照期間，則<span style=\"color: red;\">只需其中一名軍裝<br />\n警務人員按要求出示委任證</span>便可。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n728  上環見<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a21b4db6d3df2485c02914ba18e841c9907b3b8b","tid":1375052,"uid":49028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gerYRJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgerYRJr.png&h=014545a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fde2fd469abe1f53858103a0fea87d04fb5eb1c","tid":1375052,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"987085d28b2c70c8d8640714404a0de6ad576cbb","tid":1375052,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"757991c0ce7a4ee4b26b35dfbf6a4dcaae6dbac1","tid":1375052,"uid":278201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"180e711239837fb3645d79b48734fd22f3db1316"